Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.00,0:01:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創界山是分了七層\N由神僊居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.10,0:01:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了打倒支配這座山的\N邪惡帝皇多惡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.67,0:01:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一邊在各界層\N與多惡達的魔神戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.57,0:01:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一邊向第七界層前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.64,0:01:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把前六個界層\N恢復了原狀的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.15,0:01:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在往第七界層的途中\N在魔幻境迷失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.48,0:01:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要離開這個世界\N就要通過四道魔幻地獄門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.00,0:02:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進入了第一道魔幻門的我\N竟回到了我原本的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.09,0:02:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把創界山和大家的事忘記了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.63,0:02:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全靠遇見火美子\N才令我記起一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.80,0:02:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把魔道門的守護魔神沙多根\N打倒後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.77,0:02:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於可走出這道門,好\N跟著到第二道門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.44,0:02:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也會是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.84,0:02:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十四話\N難題、奇題、魔風門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.00,0:02:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,快點通過四道門啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.39,0:02:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們兩個現在在哪裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.40,0:02:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真焦燥,就是因為\N我們不知道才這麼焦慮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.40,0:02:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在就如在砧板上的肉一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.20,0:02:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!麻婆豆腐!快出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.24,0:02:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的名字是麻婆\N沒有豆腐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.15,0:03:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我特別為你弄了\N吃吧,魔婆豆腐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.25,0:03:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好熱,好熱!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.19,0:03:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺到熱只是現在罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.29,0:03:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到你的頭分開的時候\N就不覺得熱也不覺冷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.43,0:03:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真貪吃,這時間竟還有食慾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.87,0:03:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你吃太多會令你的臉孔更大\N令你更不能出外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.31,0:03:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是肚子餓就不能戰鬥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.98,0:03:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果連頭也沒有\N怎填肥肚子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.72,0:03:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是呢,渡,你在哪裏啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.66,0:03:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,有沒有人認識渡啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.89,0:03:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔,我認識啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.30,0:03:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子,渡怎樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.20,0:03:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已過了最初的魔道門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.00,0:04:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魔道門,做得好\N剩下的還有三道門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.48,0:04:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呢,過了之後\N再告訴你們吧,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.09,0:04:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蠢…蠢材!\N會有人這樣就走了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.02,0:04:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子,救我們出來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是什麼構造的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.43,0:04:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的\N真想看看她父親是什麼樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.30,0:04:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要看你就看飽它吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.94,0:04:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子那傢伙\N在這麼忙的時候去了哪裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.98,0:04:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.65,0:04:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去了哪裏啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.95,0:04:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去了看大叔他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.82,0:04:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?他們精神嗎?\N現在不是問這些事的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.92,0:04:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有這個空閒的話\N不如快點通過魔幻地獄門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.19,0:04:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你先走不是就好了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.20,0:04:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,害怕一個人去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.57,0:05:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別胡說\N我晚上可以一個人上廁所的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.24,0:05:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡很厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.41,0:05:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以不摸我的頭嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.28,0:05:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你明白就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.94,0:05:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起…\N為什麼我要道歉啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.55,0:05:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,已和同伴不和了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.29,0:05:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是,好了\N麻婆,下一道門在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.36,0:05:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在你面前\N我面前?你說在我面前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.36,0:05:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.70,0:05:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍法,和霧說再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.99,0:05:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻婆!\N渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.42,0:05:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魔幻地獄門的\N第二道門是魔風門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.83,0:06:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魔風門?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.76,0:06:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要通過這道門就要\N擊倒住在裏面的可怕怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.27,0:06:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名字就是魔之風之谷的馬鹿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.84,0:06:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魔之風之谷的馬鹿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.01,0:06:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬?鹿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.45,0:06:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旅程中的教室漢字堂開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.48,0:06:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬和鹿用漢字寫出來\N會變成「傻瓜」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.59,0:06:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以怪物的名字\N只用發音,是馬鹿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.09,0:06:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正是如此\N你要把那像木乃伊和殭屍…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.67,0:06:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,是比他們還恐怖的\N馬鹿打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.64,0:06:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果做不到…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.14,0:06:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就沒有命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.11,0:06:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怪物馬鹿\N不論有多可怕的怪物在等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.69,0:07:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要去,要在武一郎師傅\N和火美子的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.42,0:07:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人頭落地前救出他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.66,0:07:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子,你捉緊我後面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.82,0:07:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉緊那岩石,捉緊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.90,0:07:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏的風真強\N「傻瓜」在哪裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.97,0:07:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是「傻瓜」\N是馬鹿,馬鹿!你在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.97,0:07:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰在叫我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.05,0:08:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把渡他們捲走的是魔力之風\N是魔風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.79,0:08:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,落地失敗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.59,0:08:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.80,0:08:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害,是石人像呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.94,0:08:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.21,0:08:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是眼,火美子,小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.89,0:08:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬鹿!快出來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.89,0:08:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?奇怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.83,0:08:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一點也沒有向前進啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.07,0:08:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.07,0:08:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.91,0:09:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你在玩什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.68,0:09:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰在玩啊\N那裏有些什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.88,0:09:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的呢,好,我也要試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.13,0:09:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看吧,是有空氣牆嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.86,0:09:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍法,螃蟹走法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.75,0:09:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡\N在這一帶一直延續下去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.09,0:09:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說是不能再前進的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.82,0:09:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍法,破牆之術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.00,0:10:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個也不行啊\N一點傷也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬鹿,你在的話就出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.84,0:10:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救世主戰部渡要打倒你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.61,0:10:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.37,0:10:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什…什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.70,0:10:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是馬?是鹿?\N住口!你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.54,0:10:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擁有打倒多惡達拯救創界山\N使命的救世主戰部渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.55,0:10:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那又怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.05,0:10:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬鹿\N從那空氣牆過來分過高下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.25,0:10:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要通過魔風門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.36,0:10:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,如果你能解決\N我所出的三條問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.56,0:11:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解決之後就令牆消失吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.83,0:11:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對\N但是只要有一題解決不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.20,0:11:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會變成\N排在那裏的我的收藏品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.64,0:11:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說變成石像呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.21,0:11:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我用魔風把下界的人帶來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.01,0:11:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有一個不變成石像的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.45,0:11:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩子,你是第一個\N怎樣?要挑戰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.65,0:11:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然了\N我一定可以把你打倒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.34,0:11:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世伯,渡他們已通過\N第二道門了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.37,0:11:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在只有等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.81,0:11:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是大年紀的人\N很冷靜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.98,0:11:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信他們兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.75,0:11:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎,在下也要以平常心\N等待渡來救我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.69,0:12:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,用平常心等待啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.83,0:12:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!快點回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.43,0:12:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趕快啊!\N小渡,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.27,0:12:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!來吧\N最初是比力量還是死鬥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.38,0:12:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼想死嗎?那我來了\N最初是…來唱歌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.85,0:12:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最擅長唱卡拉OK了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.32,0:12:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.73,0:12:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要令那蠟燭的火\N不熄滅地唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有這種事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.14,0:12:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要唱到完為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.94,0:12:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會起風令它熄掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.81,0:12:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信我吧\N有意見的話不唱也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.21,0:13:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼…1號,戰部渡\N唱的是「Step」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.59,0:13:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點唱!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.29,0:13:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你最後流淚的理由是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.83,0:13:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太小聲了,會失去資格的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.00,0:13:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為彩虹橋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.74,0:13:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失格!\N糟了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交換!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.08,0:13:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2號,忍部火美子\N唱的是「灼熱的冒險」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.15,0:14:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.42,0:14:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.29,0:14:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是為什麼\N唱得那麼大聲火也沒有熄?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.72,0:14:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直有在學民謠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.79,0:14:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唱民謠的人會練習\N令蠟燭的火不搖動地唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.00,0:14:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一題合格了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.71,0:14:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二題了,這次是很難的\N要一次就把線穿過那針孔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.88,0:14:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼小的孔只可試一次?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.58,0:14:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,只有一次\N我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.89,0:14:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍法,穿線之術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.30,0:14:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真卑鄙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.43,0:15:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不滿意不干也可以\N好了,這次到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.28,0:15:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你失敗的話\N兩人也會變石像啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.42,0:15:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是現在了!可惡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.02,0:15:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不搖的話…對了,馬鹿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要把線穿過去就行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.50,0:15:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊\N好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.57,0:15:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿過了\N你沒說過不准碰這針呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.18,0:15:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟發現了這點\N第二題也合格了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.25,0:15:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了,渡很厲害呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.99,0:15:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣最後的問題會非常難啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.56,0:15:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用這繩把風捉住,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.53,0:16:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用這個可以捉到風嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.20,0:16:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.34,0:16:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是沒可能的難題\N怎麼辦才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.35,0:16:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,限時只剩下十分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.65,0:16:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦才好?\N用網捉住就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.06,0:16:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是用網,是用繩\N網?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.07,0:16:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,火美子\N你可以用忍法做出肥皂泡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.07,0:16:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以啊\N好,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.44,0:16:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍法,肥皂泡滿天飛之術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.71,0:16:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比較舊式呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.58,0:16:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只剩下一分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.45,0:16:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在要捉了,看著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.00,0:17:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是玩肥皂泡的時候嗎?\N只剩下30秒就變石像了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.74,0:17:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現正在捉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.00,0:17:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉到了,風就在肥皂泡裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.35,0:17:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡…合格了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.52,0:17:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等,逃得掉嗎?等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.16,0:17:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只有頭腦卻沒有體力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.83,0:17:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護魔風門的魔神\N骷髏惡魔,出來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.82,0:17:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.11,0:17:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.56,0:18:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍雷拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.47,0:18:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛龍拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.07,0:18:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,不要大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.41,0:19:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?\N它可以把身體分成兩邊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.52,0:19:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就用龍王丸分勝負吧\N來吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.46,0:19:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力量全開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.44,0:19:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變身!龍王丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.84,0:20:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變形!鳳凰!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.48,0:20:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,風牙彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.62,0:20:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,是時候了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.35,0:20:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變形!龍王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.47,0:20:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.55,0:20:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳳龍劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.74,0:21:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬鹿!就算躲起來也沒用的\N快出來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.27,0:21:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家也恢復原狀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.80,0:21:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只剩下兩道門了\N好,趕快到下一道門吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.10,0:21:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趕快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.35,0:22:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不知道之後\N有多可怕的東西在等著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.39,0:22:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧,渡,地獄在等你啊

